  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Font D’Argent is offered on a half board basis with an excellent hot and cold buffet breakfast including fruit, juices, pastries, selection of breads, local cold meats, eggs and omelettes.  Dinner consists of a 3 course buffet including high quality Mediterranean dishes and local Andorran products. Vegetarian options on the buffet are available. </p>
<p>A Christmas and New Year's Eve buffet dinner and New Year party included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
