  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Font D’Argent has established itself as the leading hotel in Pas. This modern hotel offers very good standards of accommodation and excellent local cuisine in a central village location. </p>
<h2>Soothing spa facilities</h2>
<p><span>The snow and a spa visit are the perfect combination, offering an ideal way to conclude a day filled with skiing or other winter activities. At Hotel Font d'Argent you will find 2 jacuzzis, 2 Finnish saunas and 2 Turkish saunas for your best after ski relaxation. And if you feel like pampering yourself, you can treat yourself to one of the massages or beauty treatments on offer, leaving your muscles feeling like new.</span></p>
<h2>Location </h2>
<p>Hotel Font D’Argent is located in the centre of Pas de la Casa resort, only 50 metres from the ski lifts and slopes. The ski school meeting points are conveniently located at the bottom of the lifts so getting to where you need to be in the mornings is simple and easy. There is also a bus stop located 100 metres from the property if you feel like venturing out towards the capital, Andorra la Vella. </p>
<h2>Restaurant</h2>
<p><span>Start your morning right with the breakfast buffet which offers an extensive selection of options, allowing you to pick from a range of bread, pastries, omelettes, cereals, fruits, and refreshing juices – everything you require to kickstart your day ready for the slopes. As evening falls, dinner is inspired by Mediterranean and traditional Andorran cuisine with a range of meats, fish, salads, and vegetables that will surely captivate your palate.</span></p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
